        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "### Top 5 Ligand Classes by Number of Ligands\n\n| Rank | Ligand Class | Ligand Count | % of Total |\n|------|-------------|-------------|------------|\n| 1 | Ligands not selected | 1,339 | 23.3% |\n| 2 | Amino Acids | 297 | 5.2% |\n| 3 | Aliphatic amines | 250 | 4.4% |\n| 4 | Pyridines (azines) | 248 | 4.3% |\n| 5 | Carboxylic acids | 182 | 3.2% |\n\n> **Note:** \"Ligands not selected\" is a catch-all for ligands that haven't been assigned to a specific class. If we exclude it, the 5th spot goes to **Aza-macrocycles** (165 ligands, 2.9%).",
